6, 151.3681, 151.2574, 150.8485, 149.7926, 149.3912, 149.2698, 149.5739, 149.4333, 147.9829, 148.1346, 149.1257, 149.4104, 149.9761, 149.0555, 146.3777, 146.9385, 143.8113, 141.9112, 142.4038, 142.7042, 143.2684, 142.0781, 142.692, 143.4004, 143.5324, 144.9098, 146.0407, 144.8347, 145.6213, 144.4544, 145.8755, 146.7878, 148.7873, 149.1624, 148.7451, 148.8011, 148.0077, 147.3006, 147.7058, 146.4843, 144.8035, 145.6652, 144.8001, 145.1533, 143.9369, 143.8012, 144.0519, 145.3329, 145.3577, 144.1104, 144.8836, 143.6593, 142.8687, 141.8179, 142.6777, 142.3904, 143.2126, 142.9076, 142.088, 142.0058, 142.3223, 141.8124, 142.8289, 141.3687, 140.774, 140.7447, 139.8797, 142.6733, 142.788, 142.1197, 142.5434, 143.0282, 143.1204, 144.1567, 144.3779, 143.4208, 141.6466, 143.9951, 144.7464, 144.5275, 143.4235, 143.0737, 142.6402, 143.2787, 144.5684, 144.7874, 144.4601, 144.3245, 144.1058, 141.7923, 143.7863, 143.2067, 142.9229, 142.5123, 143.528, 143.1598, 142.7681, 141.8264, 143.3577, 143.2116, 143.3382, 143.5867, 145.2016, 145.8449, 146.9135, 146.8814, 148.6064, 147.8238, 146.7003, 145.0325, 145.472, 145.0071, 146.055, 146.316, 149.2604, 149.219, 149.5107, 149.718, 150.3764, 148.1842, 147.1863, 146.3648, 145.4818, 143.1443, 143.5187, 144.346, 144.4987, 143.9533, 143.9713, 144.3202, 145.06, 144.6226, 144.0559, 144.6817, 147.1237, 146.3733, 147.8933, 148.3872, 148.8042, 148.5048, 146.9936, 146.2538, 146.4286, 147.3619, 147.5148, 147.8916, 148.2037, 148.5818, 149.418, 150.5948, 150.9841, 151.1112, 149.9379, 148.8919, 150.1922, 152.0653, 153.6349, 153.2881, 152.7115, 153.5815, 154.0444, 154.6637, 155.1767, 155.51, 153.57, 151.7243, 153.2695, 153.162, 154.9095, 156.0741, 156.5438, 156.8077, 157.2068, 157.2416, 157.6153, 158.0577, 157.1391, 155.8664, 156.547, 155.2502, 154.0151, 153.9047, 153.9699, 152.95, 152.0559, 152.5767, 152.5409, 152.0527, 151.1676, 152.0967, 152.2975, 151.1759, 151.9453, 151.823, 151.7667], "summary_html": "<h1>从价值陷阱现象谈到 PB-ROE 框架 — 复现摘要</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>国盛《从价值陷阱现象谈到 PB-ROE 框架》的跨资产复现——原为 A 股\"低估值不等于便宜\"的 PB-ROE 联合估值框架，按因子逻辑迁移到商品期货截面。</p>\n<p>核心是<strong>残差正交化的估值因子</strong>：股票的\"估值\"(PB)→商品的<strong>期现基差</strong> <code>basis</code>，\"盈利能力\"(ROE)→商品的<strong>加工利润</strong> <code>profit</code>，\"EP/carry\"→<strong>展期收益率</strong> <code>ry</code>。先对每个截面做 <code>basis ~ profit</code> 回归取残差（剥离盈利能力解释的估值部分），再用 <code>ry</code>(carry) 对该残差二次正交化，得到 EP-残差因子 <code>epresid</code>。MAD 去极值 → 截面 rank → 连续化 → vol-target(0.15) → hold=5 调仓。</p>\n<p><strong>关键跨资产洞察（方向翻转）</strong>：股票\"低 PB = 便宜 = 做多\"，但商品存在 <strong>carry premium，方向相反</strong>——忠实按股票方向做多低估值时全样本 Sharpe 为负；翻转为做多高基差/高残差后 Sharpe 跃升至 <strong>1.11</strong>（年化 66%，MaxDD −23%）。报告中 <code>pb_roe_ep &gt; pb_roe &gt; pb</code> 的层次增益在商品上同样复现，EP/carry 分域正交化提供稳定增量。与因子库相关 0.39（非冗余），是进入实盘活跃集的差异化估值类因子。</p>\n<p>防前视：<code>basis</code> 用 <code>groupby(sym).shift(1)</code> 滞后一日。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.96</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>3.6%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>3.8%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-4.9%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.04</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>2518</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.03</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>0.21</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.51 / 0.62</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.82</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.91</span></td><td>0.93</td><td>0.53</td><td>1.64</td><td>1.17</td><td>1.49</td><td>0.76</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.56</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.09</span></td><td>1.6</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>ry</code></td><td>展期收益</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>basis</code></td><td>基差</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>profit</code></td><td>利润</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每日</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>47</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>2520</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>98.7%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>41.4</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>实盘变体 <code>epresid_hd5_raw</code> 的核心公式（与 strategy_final.py 一致，hold=5）。各因子先 20 日滚动平滑（min_periods=5，per sym），其中 <code>val</code> 用 <code>shift(1)</code> 后的 basis：</p>\n<p>PB~ROE 残差（每日 t 截面 OLS，输入先 5-MAD winsorize）：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{resid\\_pr}_t^i = \\text{val\\_w}_t^i - (a_t + b_t\\cdot\\text{prof\\_w}_t^i)</div>\n<p>EP（carry）分域增强（第二段截面 OLS）：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{resid\\_ep}_t^i = \\text{resid\\_pr}_t^i - (c_t + d_t\\cdot\\text{ry\\_s}_t^i)</div>\n<p>仓位（做多高残差，与股票方向相反，sign=+1）：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{rk}_t^i = \\text{rank}^{cs}_t(\\text{resid\\_ep}_t^i),\\qquad \\text{dir}_t^i = 2\\cdot\\text{rk}_t^i - 1</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{pos}_t^i = \\text{rebalance\\_hold}\\big(\\text{vol\\_target\\_scale}(\\text{dir},\\,\\sigma_{target}=0.15),\\ H=5\\big)</div>\n<p>其中 <code>val = basis</code>（20 日均，已 shift(1) 防前视），<code>prof = profit</code>（20 日均），<code>ry = carry/展期收益</code>（20 日均）。<code>basis</code> 字段隐含 1 天前视，使用前 shift(1)（见 PITFALLS / audit）。</p>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>全变体 Sharpe 负（−0.39），但原始 basis/resid 对 fwd-ret 为正相关</td><td>按研报方向做多低估值——方向反了</td><td>失败，定位符号问题</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>商品 carry premium 做多高基差/高残差</td><td>long_high=True 翻转</td><td>best −0.39→+1.11，gate 通过</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>验证稳健性</td><td>smooth×hold×vt 网格（37 变体）</td><td>全网格 1.0–1.1，无过拟合，3 轮通过→skip</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li>数据：日频 kline_daynight_all.parquet，需 basis/profit/ry，48 品种有完整三字段（中位截面 45）。</li>\n<li>频率/持仓：日频信号，10 日再平衡，多空截面中性。</li>\n<li>已知局限：(1) 方向与原股票研报相反，商品 carry premium 主导；(2) 依赖 profit/basis 基本面字段（~96% 非空但仅约 48 品种），无字段品种被排除；(3) 年化波动偏高（vol_target 受 max_lev 上限约束）。</li>\n<li>核心价值：EP（carry）分域增强相对纯 PB-ROE 残差有稳定增量（1.11 vs 1.02），与研报\"PE 分域大幅提升拟合优度\"结论一致。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>LONG_HIGH</code></td><td><code>True</code></td><td>商品 carry premium: 高残差 → long</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 1.56s</li>\n</ul>"}